                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2021-29425&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CVE-2021-29425&lt;/a&gt; all the commons-io versions below 2.7 are affected.&lt;/p&gt;

